        <td width="300"><p class="grownups_bold_red">Printing the templates</p> <p class="instruct_normal">The first step of the activity is to print out the three game templates. Since you need at least two identical cards to play the game, you should print each template two times.</p> <p class="instruct_normal">Click on each of the template thumbnails on the left, one by one. A new page will appear with the full size template.</p> <p class="instruct_normal">Use the print function of your browser to print out each template.</p></td>
