       <tr>
        <td colspan="3"><p class="grownups_bold_red">How to play the game:</p> <p class="instruct_normal">Now that you have finished assembling your new memory game, it is time to have fun and play. The rules are simple and fun:</p>
         <ol>
          <li type="1" class="instruct_normal">Put all your cards face down on the floor or a table.</li>
          <li type="1" class="instruct_normal">Now try to match each card with its double.</li>
          <li type="1" class="instruct_normal">Turn a card to see the drawing on it. Turn another to see if it matches the first one.</li>
          <li type="1" class="instruct_normal">If it doesn't, turn the cards face down again and try with another card.</li>
          <li type="1" class="instruct_normal">The trick is to remember the drawings of the cards you turned before and to try to match all the cards.</li>
